 I.P.O while the accused statement was tendered as an exhibit. The accused spoke through his lawyer Mr Yinka Opaleke and called no witness. Vanguard News Nigeria. Ado-Ekiti- It was too late for Ojo Ayodele,to turn the hand of clock backward as nemesis finally caught up with him, when an Ado-Ekiti High Court sentenced him to life imprisonment for abducting and raping a 15-year-old girl (name withheld). May 13, 2017 In "News" Rotimi Ojomoyela - Ado-Ekiti An Ado-Ekiti High Court on Monday sentenced a 30-year-old man, Ishau Gruma to life imprisonment for raping a 6 yrs old girl. In his judgment, justice Adekunle Adeleye said the victim's father's statement, the medical report of the victim, the accused confessional statement, and his requestâ€¦ July 27, 2020 In "News" An Ado-Ekiti High Court on Tuesday sentenced a school proprietor, Ibitoye Babatunde to 10 years imprisonment for raping a 10-year-old girl. March 29, 2016 In "News"